title: Nefes: Vatan Sagolsun
overview: Story of 40-man Turkish task force who must defend a relay station.

title: Raazi
overview: A Kashmiri woman agrees to marry a Pakistani army officer in order to spy on Pakistan during the Indo-Pakistan War of 1971.

title: Yôjinbô
overview: A crafty ronin comes to a town divided by two criminal gangs and decides to play them against each other to free the town.

title: Dirty Harry
overview: When a madman calling himself "the Scorpio Killer" menaces the city, tough-as-nails San Francisco Police Inspector "Dirty" Harry Callahan is assigned to track down and ferret out the crazed psychopath.

title: Casino Royale
overview: After earning 00 status and a licence to kill, Secret Agent James Bond sets out on his first mission as 007. Bond must defeat a private banker funding terrorists in a high-stakes game of poker at Casino Royale, Montenegro.

title: Du rififi chez les hommes
overview: Four men plan a technically perfect crime, but the human element intervenes...

title: Tropa de Elite 2: O Inimigo Agora é Outro
overview: After a prison riot, former-Captain Nascimento, now a high ranking security officer in Rio de Janeiro, is swept into a bloody political dispute that involves government officials and paramilitary groups.

title: Huo Yuan Jia
overview: A biography of Chinese Martial Arts Master Huo Yuanjia, who is the founder and spiritual guru of the Jin Wu Sports Federation.

title: Udta Punjab
overview: A story that revolves around drug abuse in the affluent north Indian State of Punjab and how the youth there have succumbed to it en-masse resulting in a socio-economic decline.

title: Lat sau san taam
overview: A tough-as-nails cop teams up with an undercover agent to shut down a sinister mobster and his crew.

title: Léon
overview: Mathilda, a 12-year-old girl, is reluctantly taken in by Léon, a professional assassin, after her family is murdered. An unusual relationship forms as she becomes his protégée and learns the assassin's trade.

title: Rio Bravo
overview: A small-town sheriff in the American West enlists the help of a cripple, a drunk, and a young gunfighter in his efforts to hold in jail the brother of the local bad guy.

title: White Heat
overview: A psychopathic criminal with a mother complex makes a daring break from prison and leads his old gang in a chemical plant payroll heist.

title: Boksuneun naui geot
overview: A recently laid off factory worker kidnaps his former boss' friend's daughter, hoping to use the ransom money to pay for his sister's kidney transplant.

title: Batoru rowaiaru
overview: In the future, the Japanese government captures a class of ninth-grade students and forces them to kill each other under the revolutionary "Battle Royale" act.

title: Le salaire de la peur
overview: In a decrepit South American village, four men are hired to transport an urgent nitroglycerine shipment without the equipment that would make it safe.

title: Goldfinger
overview: While investigating a gold magnate's smuggling, James Bond uncovers a plot to contaminate the Fort Knox gold reserve.

title: Das Boot
overview: The claustrophobic world of a WWII German U-boat; boredom, filth and sheer terror.

title: The Imitation Game
overview: During World War II, the English mathematical genius Alan Turing tries to crack the German Enigma code with help from fellow mathematicians.

title: The Bourne Ultimatum
overview: Jason Bourne dodges a ruthless C.I.A. official and his Agents from a new assassination program while searching for the origins of his life as a trained killer.
